game.name: Newspaper Boy 2
game.description:
Newspaper Boy is back with more destruction and mischievous mayhem. In this latest Newspaper Boy 2, the journey of this mischievous kid starts from throwing the destructive TNT and dynamite at the neighborhood homes. Quite similar to Paperboy, this exclusively-designed racing game is a sequel to the classic. Get ready to experience the unlimited fun and craziness while being played this cycle game. 

In this hugely popular flash game, you have to break windows to collect the maximum possible combos, gather coins as well as ignore the hurdles during the extremely destructive path. You do not want to take a chance to make the wrong decision. Select your own style, aim and do not forget to upgrade your BMX bike in order to ensure your win at the end of this flash game. Get on your bike and ready to deliver the dynamite!

In this free online bicycle game for boys, you as a gamer lover have to take a chance to watch more carnage and destruction. The bike moves forward automatically. All you need to use the keys A And D to move your player in the left and right direction.  Be quick and open your mind since lots of things are out there on your way to harm your bicycle. You can aim and shoot the newspapers with the help of your mouse. In order to earn the maximum possible money, do more explosions. The points you collect are changed into dollars after each level. You can use that money to upgrade your power and bike.
